<directive id="single-function-command-files">
    The files in the commands directory may only contain one function.
</directive>

<directive id="glob-pattern-ignore-support">
    The ignore file functionality in the coder module should support ** glob pattern. 
</directive>

<directive id="no-support-for-windows">
    Don't add support for Windows. We only need to support UNIX like system, such as Linux and MacOS. 
</directive>
